Package: arcpt
Title: Changepoint Detection in Autoregressive and Regression Models
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Atharv", "Raskar", email = "atharv.raskar@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Comprehensive changepoint detection for autoregressive time series
    and regression models. Supports AR(1) and AR(2) models with optional
    trend components, mixed effects models with hierarchical data structures,
    and non-parametric regression using B-splines and natural splines.
    Uses PELT and AMOC algorithms for efficient changepoint detection.
    Implements the novel fixed vs changing covariates framework for
    generalized changepoint regression. This package was developed as part
    of the GSoC 2026 application for the "Generalized Changepoint Regression"
    project under the R Project for Statistical Computing.
License: GPL-3
